In a large microwave safe bowl, heat margarine and marshmallows at HIGH for 3 minutes, stirring after 2 minutes. Stir in vanilla. Stir in KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal until well coated. Using lightly buttered spatula, press into buttered 3.5 L (13 x 9") pan. Cool completely. Remove from pan and place on foil lined cutting board. Using red decorating gel, make a straight line down the centre of the square. Using prepared frosting make a heart on one side of the line, and on the other write a personalized greeting with red decorating gel. For a finishing touch, trim the edges using prepared frosting.